!!!
%html{:xmlns => "http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"}
  %head
    %meta{:content => "text/html; charset=ISO-8859-1", "http-equiv" => "Content-Type"}/
    %title Notificaciones SOCIAL TARGET!
    :css
      .style1 { font-size: 14px; font-family: Calibri; }
      .style2 { font-size: 12px; font-family: Calibri; color: #666666; }
      .style3 { color: #333333 }
      .style4 { font-size: 14px; font-family: Calibri; color: #333333; }
  %body
    %p.style1
      = image_tag attachments['logo.jpg'].url
    %p.style1
      %br/
      %span.style3

    %p.style4
      Social Target® te informa que tienes un nuevo referido!
    %p.style4
      - if @referral.role == 'influencer'
        = "#{@referral.influencer.full_name} (#{link_to("@" + @referral.twitter_screen_name, "http://twitter.com/#!/" + @referral.twitter_screen_name)}"
      - elsif @referral.role == 'advertiser'
        = "#{@referral.advertiser.to_s}"
      se ha registrado en el sitio y ahora es parte de tus referidos.
    %p.style4 Gracias por elegirnos,
    %p.style4
      = image_tag attachments['sellochico.jpg'].url
    %p.style4
      \--The Social Target Team
      %br/
      %em It’s time to go social!
      %br/
      %a{:href => "http://www.social-target.net"} http://www.social-target.net
    %p.style2 © 2012, Social Target Corporation